## Feature Heatmap by Discipline

![Feature Heatmap](figures/fig_feature_heatmap.png)

Different disciplines show distinct feature preferences:

- **Computer Science:** High code block and script usage
- **Mathematics:** TikZ diagrams, Algebrite, formulas
- **Language Learning:** Audio, TTS, quizzes
- **Natural Sciences:** GeoGebra, simulations

